{"tid":1090820,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖有字][毒撚岀城]6日5夜遊泰國[半live]","createTime":"2019-04-03T17:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T01:14:41.000Z","uid":23689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"530387a3cff51857718ecc2dfa6746bfddf7f315","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今次係小弟第三次去旅行<br />\n第一次去泰國，第一次膽粗粗開post<br />\n用字唔好，影相唔好請將就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機:CX<br />\n筆直:5000，唔計機票住宿<br />\n影機:iPhone XS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程:芭提雅，曼谷<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n列牌打卡位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKcc6dW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKcc6dW.png&h=d41d73ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n健康早餐，基本上得杯咖啡係有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011337_c736be5a53f59adfe6646bc1ae8df6bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011337_c736be5a53f59adfe6646bc1ae8df6bb.png&h=39a4f9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係望岀窗之前，一路坐已經感覺到有陣熱氣係背脊<br />\n望岀去已經差唔多到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011339_fc03ed256fc3b4ff1892b2f839d4ca08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011339_fc03ed256fc3b4ff1892b2f839d4ca08.png&h=b802840f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落機之後第一時間換錢<br />\n機場內匯率大概3.5到3.9不等，芭提雅亦見過4.02<br />\n跟住就緊係call車去villa<br />\n呢款車坐到成9個人，相當闊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車程大約2個鐘，收費大約3千<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011341_e6f468e6d13f40356e66dc35c5a9c8e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011341_e6f468e6d13f40356e66dc35c5a9c8e1.png&h=aee5adcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中途亦有幾陣過雲雨，沿途見到好多爛地<br />\n感覺有小小似大陸鄉村<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011343_5d3c3ba28532e22c890a22e1adf3eecd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011343_5d3c3ba28532e22c890a22e1adf3eecd.png&h=af6929ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐左2粒鐘終於到，姐姐亦拎匙黎比我地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6E3tzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6E3tzA.png&h=fec28e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011346_2d83b7d67e4e8f7122931583ad1dcdab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011346_2d83b7d67e4e8f7122931583ad1dcdab.png&h=505bac55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/04/011349_1d21f04976c6bff69d519310bc94295a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2F011349_1d21f04976c6bff69d519310bc94295a.png&h=d5a3f176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面總共5間房，個廳已經等同香港鞋盒屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜我豬西無影到入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下有無機會補翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"368aa6b7952e049e2a38fde9e9379bebe82ba652","tid":1090820,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"流明"},{"pid":"ba5bfc9934c2d8074afe42685e7e8541d4049934","tid":1090820,"uid":84250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c659f6676e5c6269ece73a52cedc1c6f4dbf52b5","tid":1090820,"uid":25566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T23:51:34.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"a504c441c124608499448deb3fb59ecd80f4d915","tid":1090820,"uid":125714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"流明"},{"pid":"c92b8d105e4c1bf802bf9fc91dbc6392d362107d","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"搬好行李自然去醫肚<br />\n由於villa 多數係鄉效地方<br />\n我地成班柒仔就決下係附近是但搵間餐廳就得<br />\n不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhX8JJi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhX8JJi.png&h=d28ce1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRhQcBK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRhQcBK.png&h=1cc7a838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9WYmu9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9WYmu9.png&h=a5b62b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成條路無遮擋，熱到傻，仲要無風<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wgA8ak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wgA8ak.png&h=819a34f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SL3Dmvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSL3Dmvu.png&h=12485e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左廿分鐘搵到個市集，開始醫肚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1z7sZhf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1z7sZhf.png&h=c62974de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6kimvH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6kimvH.png&h=4a51b10d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7167fd57065aa218dd1377c9fe21050beddc281","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"一開始我地以為間舖未開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeEGjFW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeEGjFW.png&h=00f77506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食神:啲冰有幾大粒得幾大粒<br />\n不過呢道真係要大大粒先唔易溶<br />\n另外，呢道汽水味淡過香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0OPtzq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0OPtzq.png&h=9bd99d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食方面，份量都細，要叫多幾碟先夠食<br />\n而價錢唔算貴，5個人食，基本上大約3百到4百<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyrQXsV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyrQXsV.png&h=5742a00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgBmjGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgBmjGv.png&h=aa65c3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢邊9成嘅餸菜都有辣椒<br />\n唔食得辣就叫佢少辣，不過辣得黎好過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a4c3216382300b952fa10f3145b678c21d7a19","tid":1090820,"uid":88076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"35110168be4283d7a1207db84dfef56c26ffb662","tid":1090820,"uid":57605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"等叫G report"},{"pid":"6f0b5a0d1b7610220f1d4ed780df9d5c34238f6b","tid":1090820,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"正文快開始"},{"pid":"a2e146854f46542be0f850fb5e1fe85cd8cd9556","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"醫完肚係時候起行去玩<br />\n細佬幾勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYPZU7K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYPZU7K.png&h=be05e074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一站去打真炮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7KyZzq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7KyZzq.png&h=4f160f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0J4bMer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0J4bMer.png&h=8875f36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGYzJ08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGYzJ08.png&h=b32e1dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩左.22，.9，同shortgun<br />\nShotgun 感覺好似比人左鎚咁<br />\n亦都洗得幾多錢<br />\n<br />\n行行下又食個麵頂下肚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug6BcUv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug6BcUv.png&h=2875ad7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61e0b8cecd6f045a950a10f240a31b11d51235eb","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"Keep住食野，天氣又熱夜晚都無乜胃口<br />\n於是四圍行下就算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLhXGTF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLhXGTF.png&h=67451c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係芭提雅按摩非常之平<br />\n呢個價錢，翻大陸都無喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikc1o62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fikc1o62.png&h=ef9531d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離遠影下個咸蛋黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8fb5QM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fb5QM3.png&h=f1a7abb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國老麥貴香港些小<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5b5QM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5b5QM5.png&h=4312dbe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7仔選擇亦好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以7仔亦係我地嘅晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N20BXr9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN20BXr9.png&h=b13db540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之不過，villa個微波爐原來壞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n野食變哂蒸<br />\n<br />\nDay 1完"},{"pid":"dbb8647bb91677ea4207d7a68b6ac2bf604fd19f","tid":1090820,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T22:11:04.000Z","msg":"入芭堤雅張3000？<br />\n<br />\n之前都係1500都唔洗，加得咁多"},{"pid":"bf3fca3c2e109eb78b9bd5535de0707ca25a4ec9","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb8647bb91677ea4207d7a68b6ac2bf604fd19f","tid":1090820,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T22:11:04.000Z","msg":"入芭堤雅張3000？<br />\n<br />\n之前都係1500都唔洗，加得咁多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"之後我地坐的士翻曼谷大概2200"},{"pid":"455c2665f41f348adedc7bc7148c76c4820dc940","tid":1090820,"uid":145703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5e7a92f584e2e723827e8fa7fff2ac8c3806f168","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"Day 2 開始<br />\n<br />\n黎到第2日我地決定玩下車仔<br />\n開始之前照舊搵小店醫肚<br />\n過到黎硬係覺得小店先有風味<br />\n同時好多烏蠅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPUbSnt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPUbSnt.png&h=0d9dac6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypNHY2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypNHY2z.png&h=1b61d88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZZrGf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZZrGf0.png&h=62ef836f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E24jgPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE24jgPr.png&h=8054766b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞車我覺得玩兩圈就夠，因為個軚幾硬<br />\n扭大力小小會夾手"},{"pid":"24c66bbaeda12c297cb1e3fc0b0f27d987d66fe3","tid":1090820,"uid":145703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7167fd57065aa218dd1377c9fe21050beddc281","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"一開始我地以為間舖未開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeEGjFW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeEGjFW.png&h=00f77506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食神:啲冰有幾大粒得幾大粒<br />\n不過呢道真係要大大粒先唔易溶<br />\n另外，呢道汽水味淡過香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0OPtzq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0OPtzq.png&h=9bd99d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食方面，份量都細，要叫多幾碟先夠食<br />\n而價錢唔算貴，5個人食，基本上大約3百到4百<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyrQXsV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyrQXsV.png&h=5742a00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgBmjGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgBmjGv.png&h=aa65c3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢邊9成嘅餸菜都有辣椒<br />\n唔食得辣就叫佢少辣，不過辣得黎好過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係好明點解泰國D可樂會禁淡味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似冇氣禁"},{"pid":"3a19db03495a96fcbdbe2610532bec729a30383d","tid":1090820,"uid":144085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0886987fb65307765c2fb39479ec894ef58123d8","tid":1090820,"uid":23689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"玩完車去翻步行街一帶行下商場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u21ekgX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu21ekgX.png&h=18038202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細佬我幾鍾意蝙蝠俠，見到已經忍唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/utF3dBZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FutF3dBZ.png&h=befa2874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vp0F0iX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvp0F0iX.png&h=b45e80ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img sr